35:34.666 --> 35:37.400
Are you suggesting
that Dr. Picard become

35:37.466 --> 35:39.900
a host for the organism?

35:39.966 --> 35:43.233
He would make a noble
sacrifice for science.

35:47.933 --> 35:50.300
Ginger? Ginger?

35:50.400 --> 35:51.466
Shh!

35:51.533 --> 35:52.733
I'm taking you
to a place where you can

35:52.800 --> 35:54.166
get some humanitarian help.

35:54.233 --> 35:56.666
Is this some kind of a joke?
You are one of them.

35:56.733 --> 35:58.633
