enough to hold a person.

36:06.900 --> 36:08.033
Where's your suit?

36:08.100 --> 36:10.066
It's not gonna fit
in the duct.

36:10.133 --> 36:12.266
It's alright.
I'll-I'll take my chances.

36:12.333 --> 36:14.000
Ladies first.

36:27.766 --> 36:29.133
'Okay, which way?'

36:29.200 --> 36:31.866
'I don't know,
your guess is good as mine.'

36:31.933 --> 36:33.500
'Right?'

36:33.566 --> 36:35.066
'How about left?
Straight left.'

36:35.133 --> 36:36.200
'No, I think right.
Let's go right.'

36:36.266 --> 36:38.266
'Okay, right, right, okay.'

36:38.333 --> 36:40.600
'Wait a minute. Wait a minute.
