36:40.666 --> 36:42.633
'Some light down there.'

36:42.700 --> 36:43.900
'I think I see a grid.'

36:43.966 --> 36:45.833
- 'Oh, God.'
- 'Come this way .'

36:49.233 --> 36:51.366
'Finally.
