38:20.700 --> 38:22.500
'I'm afraid the organism
has progressed much more'

38:22.566 --> 38:25.000
rapidly in this host subject.

38:28.266 --> 38:30.700
Captain, the dilithium crystals
are running out.

38:38.733 --> 38:40.866
You know how to whistle,
don't you, Steve?

38:40.933 --> 38:43.433
You just put your lips
together and...blow.

38:44.600 --> 38:46.333
This part of
the organism's progression

38:46.400 --> 38:48.900
usually doesn't last
this long.

38:55.400 --> 38:58.333
They're ba-a-ack.

38:58.400 --> 38:59.900
He should be powder by now.

39:02.333 --> 39:04.933
Live from New York, it's, ah..

39:05.000 --> 39:07.100
...Saturday night.

39:55.033 --> 39:57.166
Ah, everything your body needs.

39:57.233 --> 40:00.333
But never wanted to eat.

40:00.400 --> 40:03.200
What I wouldn't give right now
for a nice juicy steak.

40:03.266 --> 40:05.566
We'll all be dinning on real
food in just a matter of days.

40:05.633 --> 40:07.800
I wish I could
share your optimism.

40:07.866 --> 40:09.700
It isn't optimism,
it's certainty.

40:09.766 --> 40:10.766
'It's only a matter
of time before the computer'

40:10.833 --> 40:11.833
'has our answer.'

40:11.900 --> 40:13.400
And if it doesn't?

40:13.466 --> 40:16.500
I have an unshakable faith
in technology.

40:16.566 --> 40:17.900
Nice legs too.

40:18.566 --> 40:20.033
Where you going?

40:20.100 --> 40:21.966
To conduct
another interview.

40:22.033 --> 40:24.000
Maybe the last chance I get.

40:29.566 --> 40:32.100
'Computer access closes
in five minutes.'

40:32.166 --> 40:35.033
'All requests must
process through level two.'

40:37.966 --> 40:39.533
I'm taking you
out of here.

40:39.600 --> 40:41.200
What?

40:41.266 --> 40:42.500
What about them?

40:42.566 --> 40:44.533
'I exposed them
to the organism.'

40:47.133 --> 40:48.666
Then why don't we
just wait till they explode?

40:48.733 --> 40:50.866
There's no telling,
if it'll ever kill them.

40:50.933 --> 40:53.733
Thank God,
it hasn't killed you yet.

40:53.800 --> 40:56.066
I still say,
we'll never make it past them.

40:56.133 --> 40:57.300
Come with me. Wait.

40:59.133 --> 41:02.133
'Level four lock down test
commences in ten minutes.'

41:05.300 --> 41:06.733
Now is our chance.

41:24.533 --> 41:25.766
'What are you doing?'

41:25.833 --> 41:27.400
She's contaminated.

41:27.466 --> 41:29.433
Get Dr. Van Der Straten.

41:39.400 --> 41:41.800
Damn the torpedoes.
Full speed ahead!

41:49.866 --> 41:52.733
'There will be no movie in the
rest area this time around.'

41:55.333 --> 41:56.300
Made it, ma!

41:56.366 --> 41:58.733
Top of the world.

42:06.833 --> 42:08.800
Good grief!

42:11.800 --> 42:14.133
You exposed 'em
to the organism.

42:14.200 --> 42:15.800
'Haven't you?'

