43:18.933 --> 43:21.400
'Dr. Van Der Straten,
this is computer central.'

43:21.466 --> 43:22.900
'We have you results.'

43:22.966 --> 43:25.066
'Your female subject
has only one distinction'

43:25.133 --> 43:26.433
'from the other victims.'

43:26.500 --> 43:28.200
'She's been celibate
for several months'

43:28.266 --> 43:29.766
'and therefore
has a very low level'

43:29.833 --> 43:32.300
'of sexual hormones
in her system.'

43:32.366 --> 43:36.133
'Our assumption is that, if her
sexual arousal level increases'

43:36.200 --> 43:38.166
'for example,
from a sudden burst of passion'

43:38.233 --> 43:40.166
'the organism could kill her.'

43:40.233 --> 43:41.700
Uh-oh.

43:51.600 --> 43:56.200
I'll eat you, my pretty
and your little dog too.

44:04.466 --> 44:06.233
'Dr. Van Der Straten.'

44:06.300 --> 44:07.933
'Did you receive my message?'

44:09.133 --> 44:11.600
'Dr. Rostinskya,
please acknowledge.'

44:12.633 --> 44:14.233
'Is there anybody there?'

44:15.333 --> 44:16.800
'Hello?'

44:18.400 --> 44:20.033
'Hello?'

